      "sender_name": "Nobel Mount College",
      "timestamp_ms": 1757081932568,
      "content": "Network Engineering Course Outline Details\n\u00e2\u009e\u0096\u00e2\u009e\u0096\u00e2\u009e\u0096\u00e2\u009e\u0096\u00e2\u009e\u0096\u00e2\u009e\u0096\u00e2\u009e\u0096\u00e2\u009e\u0096\u00e2\u009e\u0096\u00e2\u009e\u0096\u00e2\u009e\u0096\u00e2\u009e\u0096\u00e2\u009e\u0096\u00e2\u009e\u0096\u00e2\u009e\u0096\u00e2\u009e\u0096\nModule-1 Network Fundamentals\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9 What is computer network?\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9 Smallest and largest computer network.\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9 Wired and Wireless network\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9 Network Devices\n              (Hub, Switch, Router, Bridge, Repeater, Modem, Access Point, Firewall, NIC Card)\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9Network Topologies\n              (Bus, Ring, Star, Point to Point, Point to Multipoint, Full and Partial Mesh Topology)\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9 Logical Vs Physical Topology\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9 Classification of Network \n              (LAN, CAN, MAN, WAN, SAN)\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9Data Transmission Media/Medium\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9Baseband and Broadband technology\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9Bandwidth, Throughput and Speed\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9Transmission Modes\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9MAC Address Structure and Addressing\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9TCP and UDP \n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9TCP/UDP service port numbers\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9TCP/IP Addressing\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9IPv4 Structure and Addressing \n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9Public IP and Private IP\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9IPv6 Addressing\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9OSI Reference Model\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9Encapsulation and Decapsulation of OSI 7 layer\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9 IEEE Standard\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9Ethernet Standard\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9Ethernet Cabling \n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9MDI, MDI-X, Auto-MDIX port\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9Ethernet Auto-negotiation\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9Fiber-Optic Cable\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9Ethernet Media Converters\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9CSMA/CD\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9Peer to Peer Network LAB\n                \u00e2\u0096\u00aa\u00ef\u00b8\u008f Operating System\n                     (Client operating system and Network operating system)\n                 \u00e2\u0096\u00aa\u00ef\u00b8\u008f Virtual box Installation and configuration\n                 \u00e2\u0096\u00aa\u00ef\u00b8\u008f Windows installation on Virtual box \n                 \u00e2\u0096\u00aa\u00ef\u00b8\u008f Virtual box network setting \n                 \u00e2\u0096\u00aa\u00ef\u00b8\u008f TCP/IP Utility tool\n                 \u00e2\u0096\u00aa\u00ef\u00b8\u008f Basic file sharing and SMB protocol (Lab)\n                 \u00e2\u0096\u00aa\u00ef\u00b8\u008f Hidden file sharing (Lab)\n                 \u00e2\u0096\u00aa\u00ef\u00b8\u008f Map network drive (Lab)\n                 \u00e2\u0096\u00aa\u00ef\u00b8\u008f Printer Sharing (Lab)\n                 \u00e2\u0096\u00aa\u00ef\u00b8\u008f Group policy configuration\n                 \u00e2\u0096\u00aa\u00ef\u00b8\u008f Remote features (Lab)\n                     (Remote Desktop Connection, \n                       Radmin Remote Software, Teamviewer software)\n                 \u00e2\u0096\u00aa\u00ef\u00b8\u008f Internet connection sharing (Lab)\nModule-2 Microsoft Server Administration\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9Microsoft Server 2019 Edition and License \n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9RAID Technology\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9Server 2019 installation on Virtual box\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9Initial setup on Microsoft Server 2019\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9NIC Teaming Configuration\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9Storage Pool and File Sharing with Permission\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9NAT Server Installation and Configuration\n            (PAT, Dynamic NAT, Static NAT, Port Forwarding)(LAB)\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9DHCP Server Installation and Configuration (LAB)\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9FTP Server Installation and Configuration (LAB)\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9WEB Server Installation and Configuration (LAB)\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9DNS Server Installation and Configuration (LAB)\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9Daily/ Weekly data backup and restore configuration with Backup4all Software\n   \u00f0\u009f\u0094\u00b9ADDS Server Installation and Configuration \n                    \u00e2\u0096\u00aa\u00ef\u00b8\u008f (PDC, BDC)\n                    \u00e2\u0096\u00aa\u00ef\u00b8\u008f Manage User Account, Password Policy and Account Logout Policy\n                    \u00e2\u0096\u00aa\u00ef\u00b8\u008f User Right Assignment \n                    \u00e2\u0096\u00aa\u00ef\u00b8\u008f Logon to PC and Logon hours\n                    \u00e2\u0096\u00aa\u00ef\u00b8\u008f Local User Disable\n                    \u00e2\u0096\u00aa\u00ef\u00b8\u008f Roaming user profile \n                    \u00e2\u0096\u00aa\u00ef\u00b8\u008f Manage Group Policy\n                    \u00e2\u0096\u00aa\u00ef\u00b8\u008f Server Backup and Restore",
